column5: I sent you an email about a week ago inquiring about a trip in 2007? Did you receive it? Max
I talked to the folks at Evergreen this week and they are working on putting in wireless at the camp. Might be they are having some computer problems. Try calling them at 1-888-522-7385
I just spoke to Pat and she was not near her book and said she would return my call in about an hour.....Thank You
